query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it1.info in ('rentals','LD video quality','opening weekend','LD laserdisc title','sound mix','taglines','production dates') AND k.keyword not like '%vengeance%' AND k.keyword not like '%mafia%' AND k.keyword not like '%suspense%' AND k.keyword not like '%investigate%' AND n.name not like '%C%' AND cct1.kind in ('crew','complete+verified','complete') AND it2.info in ('trade mark','LD release date','other works','LD analog left','LD audio noise','color info','LD group genre','LD original title','LD color information','locations','LD analog right','soundtrack','LD video quality','quotes','certificates','rating','copyright holder','biographical movies','release dates','salary history') AND mi.info in ('English','Hindi','Catalan','Albanian','Macedonian')
